# Insofix Development Website

This repository is the development and testing version of the Insofix Ltd website.

## Site type

Static HTML and CSS website.

## Local preview

Run from the repository root:

python3 -m http.server 4173

Then open:

http://localhost:4173

## Public pages

- index.html
- contact.html
- mortgage-problem.html
- removal-process.html
- superfoil.html

## Deployment

GitHub Pages deploys from:

- Branch: main
- Folder: /(root)

All changes must be made through a task branch and pull request.

## Safety

- Do not modify the production Insofix website.
- Do not add passwords, API keys or customer data.
- Do not merge automatically.
- Do not change the custom domain without approval.
